    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Building materials comprising cut, carved, shaped, or molded units of stone, ceramic brick or tile, concrete, glass, adobe, or other similar material.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
